              p Keep up to date with the latest discount codes and coupon offers from Park Cameras by 
                a(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/newsletter-signup-full', title='Sign up to Park Cameras') signing up to our mailing list
                |.
            
            
            // -----------------CANON----------------- //
            
            hr
            
            .pc-wrapper.pc-column.pc-col1
              h2#canon Canon Cashback &amp; Deals
            .pc-wrapper.pc-row
              .pc-column.pc-col8
                img.pc-brandImg(src='https://content.parkcameras.com/5/1/images/site_images/Canon-offers-logo.png', alt='Canon Brand Logo')
              .pc-column.pc-col2
                p Cashback, promotional offers, and discounts from Canon on DSLR cameras, lenses, mirrorless cameras, and accessories will be shown here when they are running. Individual offers and promotions are also shown on specific product pages.
