                  a(href='https://www.canon.co.uk/promotions/', target='_blank', title='Canon Promotions') visiting their promotions page
                  |. 
                
                .pc-promoBanner(data-start-date='2018-02-01' data-end-date='2018-02-28')
                  h2 Canon EOS 5D Mark IV
                  p Get &pound;200 trade-in bonus when you trade in qualifying working digital interchangeable lens camera for the 
                    a(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/p/1010055C', title='Canon EOS 5D Mark IV') Canon EOS 5D Mark IV
                    |.
                  p
                    small Promotion valid 01/02/18 - 28/02/18
                
                .pc-promoBanner(data-start-date='2018-01-19' data-end-date='2018-02-28')
                  h2 Canon EOS M100
                  p Save &pound;50 on the 
                    a(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/search/go?w=canon%20eos%20m100&af=cat1:digitalcameras', title='Canon EOS M100') Canon EOS M100 Body or Kit
                    | 
                    | when you use the voucher code 
                    span(style='font-weight: 700;') CANON-50-OFF
                    | 
