                    a(href='https://www.parkcameras.com/search/go?w=canon%20eos%201300d&af=cat1:digitalcameras', title='Canon EOS 1300D') Canon EOS 1300D Body or Kit
                    | 
                    | when you use the voucher code 
                    strong CANON-30-OFF
                    | 
                    | at checkout.
                    
                  p
                    small Promotion valid 14/02/18 - 21/02/18
                    
